    {"id":1,"type":"MarkdownNote","pos":[50,50],"size":[500,320],"flags":{},"order":0,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"title":"VGA v17.2 — ComfyUI Pipeline","properties":{},"widgets_values":["## VGA v17.2 ComfyUI Pipeline — BF16 Edition\n\n**Required custom nodes (install via ComfyUI Manager):**\n- `ComfyUI-IPAdapter-Flux` (Shakker-Labs)\n- `ComfyUI-Wan-SVI2Pro-FLF` (Well-Made)\n- `ComfyUI-LatentSyncWrapper` (ShmuelRonen)\n- `ComfyUI-pause` (wywywywy)\n- `ComfyUI-MMAudio` (kijai)\n- `ComfyUI-MusicGen-HF` (ebrinz)\n- `CosyVoice-ComfyUI` or `ComfyUI_FL-CosyVoice3`\n\n**Wan2.2 BF16 models required (download from Comfy-Org repackaged):**\n- `wan2.2_i2v_high_noise_14B_bf16.safetensors` → diffusion_models/\n- `wan2.2_i2v_low_noise_14B_bf16.safetensors` → diffusion_models/\n\n**Key settings (RTX PRO 6000 96GB):**\n- Steps: **30** (STEPS_STANDARD — BF16 GPU-resident, no offload)\n- Sigma shift S-08 I2V: **5.0** (official Wan2.2 I2V recommendation)\n- Sigma shift S-09 SVI: **7.0** (SVI LoRA training distribution)\n- CFG: **7.0** (vita-epfl recommendation for non-distill SVI)\n- Denoising strength SVI: **0.72** (balanced continuation)\n- NO post-processing enhancement for BF16 (clean output, no CLAHE)\n\n**Flow:** S-05 FLUX image → S-06 LoRA reinforce → S-07 Z-Image refine → S-08 Wan2.2 BF16 I2V Seg1 → S-09 SVI BF16 Segs 2-4 → S-11 TTS → S-12 LipSync → S-13 MMAudio → S-14 MusicGen\n\n**HRG pause gates:** HRG-5 through HRG-11 (7 checkpoints)"],"color":"#222","bgcolor":"#000"},

